Redirection:
-> Input Redirection
-> Output redirection
-> Error redirection
-> Pipe redirection


input redirection:

wc large.txt
wc
output redirection:

ls
dir
input+output:
date > command.txt

error redirection:
lss
lss 2> error.txt

input+output+error redirection:
ls /Desktop /Doccument > myfile 2>&1
cat myfile
--------------------------------------------


Input Redirection:
wc file
cat > file1
cat >> file2

Output Redirection:
ls
dir
date
wc
ll

Input and output redirection:

date > file
ls > file1

Error redirection:
lss
lss 2> error.txt
ls /binn 2>> error.txt

Input output and error redirection:
ls /usr/local /binn > command.txt 2>&1
